title: Ableton Live 9 Suite Full Pack Library Sounds and Max for Live I
description:
This is the same as the "Ableton 9 Full Max for live Packs" torrent, but extracted from the triple-compressed RAR archive (that doesn't even compress them much at all anyway) and into their individual Ableton Live Pack files.

Should work on both Windows and Mac versions.
